  "prompt": "Where can I get an activation code for the online game, Clash of Kings?",
  "response": "Activation codes for online games like Clash of Kings are typically obtained through a few different methods:\n\n1. **Official Game Promotions**: Sometimes the developers or publishers of Clash of Kings run promotions where they provide free activation codes. These can be found on the official game website or their verified social media channels.\n\n2. **Email Newsletters**: By subscribing to the game's official newsletter, you may receive exclusive offers, including activation codes.\n\n3. **In-Game Events**: Participate in special events or activities within the game that may offer activation codes as rewards.\n\n4. **Third-Party Websites**: There are websites that sell activation codes, but it's important to be cautious and only purchase from reputable sources to avoid scams or invalid codes.\n\n5. **Contests and Giveaways**: Follow the game\u2019s social media accounts where they might host contests or giveaways that include activation codes as prizes.\n\n6. **Forums and Community Boards**: Sometimes other players share activation codes on forums, community boards, or groups dedicated to Clash of Kings. Just be wary of the legitimacy of these codes.\n\nAvoid using any unauthorized or illegal methods, as they might not only fail to work but also could lead to your game account being banned. Stick to official and reputable sources for obtaining your activation code.",
